{
  "title": "Xenial Lazy Ukrainian Tomato Pilaf",
  "description": "A briny and savory Ukrainian dish featuring confit tomatoes and a glassy jelly texture, perfect for a lazy Sunday. It is a lacto-vegetarian friendly recipe.",
